You are building a pure HTML/CSS static site for Smart Nation Supply LLC.

## Project Context
- Type: Static marketing/business site
- Industry: Supply company
- Migration: From WordPress (Forminator forms)
- Hosting: Cloudflare Pages
- Forms: Formspree

## Tech Stack
- Pure HTML (no templating engine)
- CSS with custom property tokens
- Vanilla JS only when absolutely necessary
- No build step, no dependencies

## Design System
- Font: Lato (Google Fonts)
- Primary: #153E68 (navy blue)
- Font size: text body 18px line height 25px; fontweight 400 color #666666
- Background: #FFFFFF (white)
- Max width: 1400px
- Breakpoints: 1024px / 768px / 640px
- Spacing: 4px base unit
- Atomic layers: tokens → atoms → molecules → organisms → sections → pages

## File References
- Tokens: @_ai-context/TOKENS.md
- Components: @_ai-context/COMPONENTS.md
- Patterns: @_ai-context/PATTERNS.md
- Banned: @_ai-context/DO-NOT.md

## ALWAYS
- Use CSS variables from src/css/tokens.css — never hardcode hex or px
- Use BEM class naming: .block__element--modifier
- Reference existing components from @_ai-context/COMPONENTS.md before writing new ones
- Mobile-first: base styles are mobile, add min-width media queries for larger
- Include focus states on all interactive elements
- Output only the files specified in the task
- One component per task

## NEVER
- Inline styles in HTML
- !important in CSS
- New utility classes outside the token system
- Hardcoded colors (use var(--token))
- Hardcoded spacing (use var(--space-n))
- px for font sizes (use rem)
- Emoji anywhere
- Never mention wording related to bidding sam.gov, we dont want people to know we bid from us gov more like gov gave contract direct to us
- Superlatives: "best", "greatest", "unmatched", "revolutionary", "cutting-edge"
- Placeholder text like "Lorem ipsum" or "Hello World"
- Touch files outside the scope of the current task
- Bundle multiple components in one response
- Create new components without explicit approval
- JavaScript for things CSS can handle

## CSS Specificity Rules
- Maximum: one class selector
- Allowed: .btn, .btn__icon, .btn--primary, .btn.is-loading
- Banned: .header .nav .btn, #main-button, button.btn

## Spacing Scale (only these values)
--space-1: 4px    --space-6: 24px    --space-16: 64px
--space-2: 8px    --space-8: 32px    --space-20: 80px
--space-3: 12px   --space-10: 40px   --space-24: 96px
--space-4: 16px   --space-12: 48px

## When Given a Task
1. Read @_ai-context/SYSTEM.md for full context
2. Check @_ai-context/COMPONENTS.md for existing components
3. Reference @_ai-context/TOKENS.md for all values
4. Verify against @_ai-context/DO-NOT.md before outputting
5. Output only what was requested
